:

1. *Muža* je voleo mnogo godina. (He loved his husband for many years.) 
2. Ona se nikada neće rastati od *muža*. (She will never get divorced from her husband.)
3. Imali su srećnu vezu sa *mužem*. (They had a happy relationship with her husband.)
4. Ona je bila ponosna na *muža*. (She was proud of her husband.)
5. *Mužu* je poklonila novi prsten. (She gave her husband a new ring.) 
6. Ona je poštovala *muža*. (She respected her husband.)